!                                                                                                   
! This test calculates the energy and some properties                                               
! of the dichloroethane molecule in different geometries.                                           
! Note that we consistently leave out the SS integrals                                              
! by using the LVCORR option in the general section.                                                
!                                                                                                   
**DIRAC                                                                                             
.TITLE                                                                                              
1,2-dichloroethane. Restricted kinetic balance. Energies, properties.                               
.WAVE F                                                                                             
.PROPER                                                                                             
**HAMILTONIAN                                                                                       
.LVCORR                                                                                             
**WAVE FUNCTIONS                                                                                    
.SCF                                                                                                
.RELCCSD                                                                                            
*SCF                                                                                                
.EVCCNV                                                                                             
1.0E-8                                                                                              
**PROPERTIES                                                                                        
.DIPOLE                                                                                             
.QUADRUPOLE                                                                                         
.NQCC                                                                                               
**RELCCSD                                                                                           
.TIMING                                                                                             
*END OF                                                                                             


