        6.    1                                                                                     
C   -0.7000 0.0000 0.0000                                                                           
LARGE BASIS cc-pVDZ                                                                                 
       17.    1                                                                                     
Cl  -1.3000 0.0000 1.6971                                                                           
LARGE BASIS cc-pVDZ                                                                                 
        1.    1                                                                                     
H   -1.0667 0.8981 -0.5185                                                                          
LARGE BASIS cc-pVDZ                                                                                 
FINISH                                                                                              


